{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/960/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/960.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/960/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/960/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/960/allow-multiple-contactsensor-per-collision"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/960/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec/5445ce6e-6273-47f0-84eb-621c86ca11cb/128"}}, "nickname": "hsu", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec"}, "title": "Allow Multiple ContactSensor per collision geometry", "component": {"name": "sensors", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/components/122877.json"}}}, "votes": 0, "watches": 4, "content": {"raw": "Currently, only one `ContactSensor` per allowed for a collision geometry as the [`ContactManager::customContactPublishers`](#!/osrf/gazebo/src/c5b1d48b8aeebf7e1ae801ef7542ec75312088d0/gazebo/physics/ContactManager.cc?at=default#cl-268) are id'd by [collision geometry's entity name](#!/osrf/gazebo/src/c5b1d48b8aeebf7e1ae801ef7542ec75312088d0/gazebo/sensors/ContactSensor.cc?at=default#cl-115).\r\n\r\nInstead, do something like\r\n~~~\r\n    std::string topic = mgr->CreateFilter(entityName+\"::\"+sensorName, this->collisions);\r\n~~~\r\nto change this behavior.\r\n\r\nThis issue was motivated by [this test world with 2 contact sensors on one collision body](https://github.com/ros-simulation/gazebo_ros_pkgs/blob/gazebo_plugins_test_world_update/gazebo_plugins/test/test_worlds/bumper_test.world).\r\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Currently, only one <code>ContactSensor</code> per allowed for a collision geometry as the <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/c5b1d48b8aeebf7e1ae801ef7542ec75312088d0/gazebo/physics/ContactManager.cc?at=default#cl-268\" rel=\"nofollow\"><code>ContactManager::customContactPublishers</code></a> are id'd by <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/c5b1d48b8aeebf7e1ae801ef7542ec75312088d0/gazebo/sensors/ContactSensor.cc?at=default#cl-115\" rel=\"nofollow\">collision geometry's entity name</a>.</p>\n<p>Instead, do something like</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>    <span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span> <span class=\"nt\">topic</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">mgr-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">CreateFilter</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">entityName</span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;::&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"nt\">sensorName</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"nt\">this-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">collisions</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>to change this behavior.</p>\n<p>This issue was motivated by <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://github.com/ros-simulation/gazebo_ros_pkgs/blob/gazebo_plugins_test_world_update/gazebo_plugins/test/test_worlds/bumper_test.world\" rel=\"nofollow\">this test world with 2 contact sensors on one collision body</a>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-11-18T23:49:52.427594+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:44:26.179864+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 960}